<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Birthday Wish</title>
</head>
<body style="background-color:#16B6FA;color:white;padding:20px;font-size:18px;">
	<h3>Hey,</h3> 

	<p>Someone on GroupWish thought you'd like to wish <%= @name %> a happy birthday, which is coming up on <%= @day %>! Please fill out your message and name below!</p>



	<form action=<%= @url %>>
		<label for="message">Message</label><br>
		<textarea name="message"></textarea><br>
		<label for="author">Author</label><br>
		<input type="text" name="author"><br>
		<input type="submit" value="Submit" style="color: white;
		      cursor: pointer;
		      border-radius: 5px;
		      border: 0;
		      margin-top: 10px;
		      width: 80px;
		      height:40px;
		      font-size: 1em;
		      background: #ffad3f;"> 
	</form>

	<p style="text-align:right;">Sincerely, <br>
		The GroupWish Team</p>
</body>
</html>